    "description": "<p>The Resolute Hunter specializes in Recruitment Search and Advisory Solutions in the sphere of the Financial Services, Banking and other Commercial industries.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We partner with you to understand your unique and varying organization needs. We endeavour to deliver steadfast recruitment services. With an intricate approach and a fervent focus, we identify, design and execute tailor-made solutions with professional integrity.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are a team of certified and experienced Search professionals with an impeccable track record in their specialized fields.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are RESOLUTE in our drive to cultivate valued partnerships with our clients and candidates. We make every experience count. Are you ready to make YOUR experience count, today?</p>\n<p><br></p>",
